==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Addendum
<hw>Ad*den"dum</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Addenda</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., fr. <ets>addere</ets>
to add.]</ety> <def>A thing to be added; an appendix or
addition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Addendum circle</b></col> <fld>(Mech.)</fld>, <cd>the
circle which may be described around a circular spur wheel or gear
wheel, touching the crests or tips of the teeth.</cd>
<rj><au>Rankine.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adder</ent>⟦br⟧
